message.text:
‪BREAKING: Manila City Mayor Francisco “Isko Moreno” Domagoso has ordered the suspension of classes starting 2:00 pm today, September 23, 2019, in celebration of the 27th National Family Week

Covered in the suspension order are classes in all levels, public and private schools‬

‪#AlertoManileno #WalangPasok ‬
